mec:retirar a owl:ObjectProperty .
mec:soltar a owl:ObjectProperty .
mec:cerrar a owl:ObjectProperty .

elec:conectarCables a owl:ObjectProperty .

hid:conectarTubosHidraulicos a owl:ObjectProperty .
neum:conectarTuboNeumatico a owl:ObjectProperty .

base:cambiarBase a owl:ObjectProperty .